// Form1.Designer.cs
// ============================================================
// This is the WinForms Designer partial class for Form1.
// It is responsible for *creating* and *laying out* UI controls.
//
// Big picture layout:
// - _split: A 2-column TableLayoutPanel
//      - Left side: calculator UI (_left)
//      - Right side: history UI (_right)
//
// Left side (_left) contains:
//  1) _inputs: Quote + optional 2nd input (CH Robinson fee)
